not only are you not her real mother,

00:00:57.200 --> 00:01:00.000
but also the one who killed her father,

00:01:03.679 --> 00:01:04.760
how would she feel?

00:01:08.840 --> 00:01:10.400
What exactly do you want?

00:01:14.319 --> 00:01:17.159
To become the head of the Tang Family,

00:01:17.400 --> 00:01:18.760
you must be clever.

00:01:19.200 --> 00:01:20.480
What I want—

00:01:21.560 --> 00:01:23.239
