00:01:34.200 --> 00:01:35.040
How is it?

00:01:42.879 --> 00:01:43.640
Let's talk outside.

00:02:01.200 --> 00:02:02.560
Her pulse is weak,

00:02:03.400 --> 00:02:04.439
but still fairly steady.

00:02:05.400 --> 00:02:07.079
It's less a coma,

00:02:07.879 --> 00:02:09.479
more like she's just asleep.

00:02:11.919 --> 00:02:12.719
That's good.

00:02:14.159 --> 00:02:14.960
I didn't expect

00:02:15.599 --> 00:02:16.919
you could read pulses.

00:02:19.199 --> 00:02:20.319
My mom is amazing.

00:02:21.319 --> 00:02:24.080
Doctors often came to ask her advice.

00:02:24.280 --> 00:02:26.759
I picked up a little bit over time.

00:02:29.080 --> 00:02:30.120
This is all my fault.

00:02:30.719 --> 00:02:32.520
If I hadn't tossed the address away,

00:02:33.080 --> 00:02:34.280
Xiao Duo wouldn't have found it.

00:02:37.360 --> 00:02:38.439
It's not your fault.

00:02:40.159 --> 00:02:41.759
That's just how Xiao Duo is.

00:02:42.879 --> 00:02:44.599
Even if she couldn't find the address,

00:02:45.240 --> 00:02:46.599
she'd find another way.

00:02:48.439 --> 00:02:49.159
Besides,

00:02:50.560 --> 00:02:52.000
if not for Xiao Duo,

00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:54.240
we wouldn't have survived.

00:02:58.360 --> 00:03:00.599
Xiao Duo called out "Brother" before fainting.

00:03:01.400 --> 00:03:02.400
Tell me,

00:03:03.280 --> 00:03:05.199
why was she silent before?

00:03:06.199 --> 00:03:08.840
Could it be related to her power?

00:03:12.599 --> 00:03:14.960
Brother

00:03:15.800 --> 00:03:16.599
Xiao Duo

00:03:19.800 --> 00:03:21.000
When will Xiao Duo wake up?

00:03:24.080 --> 00:03:26.280
She might need a full checkup at the hospital.

00:03:26.960 --> 00:03:28.080
But I guess

00:03:28.319 --> 00:03:30.280
they won't have a clear answer.

00:03:32.199 --> 00:03:33.520
I'll take her to get checked now.

00:03:39.120 --> 00:03:39.800
Xiao Duo

00:03:41.800 --> 00:03:42.599
Xiao Duo

00:03:43.840 --> 00:03:44.520
The door is locked.

00:03:46.479 --> 00:03:47.280
Xiao Duo

00:03:48.439 --> 00:03:49.039
Xiao Duo

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:51.479
No, something's wrong.

00:03:51.960 --> 00:03:52.759
Something must've happened.

00:03:53.879 --> 00:03:54.199
Move aside.

00:03:54.199 --> 00:03:55.080
Let me kick the door open.

00:03:55.240 --> 00:03:55.960
Calm down.

00:03:55.960 --> 00:03:56.599
Brother

00:04:00.360 --> 00:04:01.159
Xiao Duo

00:04:03.599 --> 00:04:04.400
Xiao Duo

00:04:05.039 --> 00:04:05.960
Open the door!

00:04:06.479 --> 00:04:07.439
Xiao Duo, open up!

00:04:09.360 --> 00:04:11.840
You must've seen how I looked.

00:04:15.360 --> 00:04:16.399
Don't worry.

00:04:16.680 --> 00:04:18.000
I'll leave on my own.

00:04:18.639 --> 00:04:19.319
Xiao Duo

00:04:20.680 --> 00:04:21.879
What are you saying?

00:04:23.279 --> 00:04:25.800
I know I looked scary.

00:04:26.399 --> 00:04:27.360
I don't know

00:04:27.360 --> 00:04:29.600
why I turned out this way.

00:04:30.600 --> 00:04:31.879
My aunt said

00:04:31.879 --> 00:04:34.279
I caused my parents' deaths.

00:04:35.399 --> 00:04:36.399
Brother Meng

00:04:37.079 --> 00:04:38.360
Sister Yuyan

00:04:39.399 --> 00:04:40.399
Sister Yuer

00:04:41.160 --> 00:04:41.959
I'm sorry.

00:04:42.160 --> 00:04:44.519
I never meant to hurt you.

00:04:46.040 --> 00:04:47.839
Xiao Duo, don't say such nonsense.

00:04:48.399 --> 00:04:49.759
Me and Brother Meng,

00:04:49.759 --> 00:04:51.399
and Sister Yuer, would never blame you.

00:04:51.959 --> 00:04:53.160
You protected us.

00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:54.800
Xiao Duo

00:04:55.600 --> 00:04:56.839
Please open the door.

00:04:57.399 --> 00:04:58.199
Open the door.

00:04:59.959 --> 00:05:00.720
Brother

00:05:01.279 --> 00:05:02.800
Are you afraid of Xiao Duo?

00:05:09.920 --> 00:05:10.480
Xiao Duo

00:05:12.600 --> 00:05:14.360
I'm the real bad guy.

00:05:16.360 --> 00:05:17.959
When we first met,

00:05:19.360 --> 00:05:20.959
you gave me your only food.

00:05:22.399 --> 00:05:23.120
But I stayed with you

00:05:23.120 --> 00:05:24.720
because being near you boosted my power.

00:05:25.279 --> 00:05:26.240
That's why I followed you.

00:05:29.879 --> 00:05:32.399
I wanted to use you at first.

00:05:33.800 --> 00:05:34.759
Xiao Duo

00:05:36.040 --> 00:05:37.519
Will you be my little sister?

00:05:41.680 --> 00:05:42.399
Back then,

00:05:42.399 --> 00:05:44.000
I didn't lead you on the right path,

00:05:45.720 --> 00:05:47.240
I used you to hide my identity.

00:05:48.079 --> 00:05:49.600
I dragged you into petty theft.

00:05:57.319 --> 00:05:59.079
I'm the one who did wrong.

00:06:00.639 --> 00:06:01.439
All these years,

00:06:02.600 --> 00:06:04.079
we've relied on each other.

00:06:05.480 --> 00:06:07.759
I've always seen you as my real sister.

00:06:12.600 --> 00:06:13.399
Xiao Duo

00:06:14.160 --> 00:06:15.079
You can scold me,

00:06:15.199 --> 00:06:16.120
or hit me,

00:06:16.920 --> 00:06:17.480
but

00:06:18.839 --> 00:06:20.600
please don't leave me.

00:06:28.920 --> 00:06:29.639
Xiao Duo

00:06:31.240 --> 00:06:32.439
We have no home now.

00:06:33.319 --> 00:06:35.160
You're all I have left.

00:07:14.480 --> 00:07:15.879
I won't cry.

00:07:20.680 --> 00:07:21.360
Young Master Shen

00:07:21.800 --> 00:07:22.759
Why

00:07:23.279 --> 00:07:23.959
did they all say

00:07:24.199 --> 00:07:25.879
the Shen Family could cure this child?

00:07:26.160 --> 00:07:27.560
We couldn't help her,

00:07:27.560 --> 00:07:29.519
so we sent her to your family.

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:31.959
Didn't the Shen Family promise us

00:07:31.959 --> 00:07:33.040
to treat her kindly?

00:07:33.560 --> 00:07:34.959
Young Master Shen, please!

00:07:36.839 --> 00:07:38.800
The Master's will is like the dawn;

00:07:39.680 --> 00:07:40.800
it cannot be obscured.

00:07:43.160 --> 00:07:43.800
This is

00:07:44.680 --> 00:07:46.680
Xiao Duo's sealed memory.

00:07:47.959 --> 00:07:49.079
Those who stand in the way—

00:07:50.079 --> 00:07:51.680
like moths eating clothes,

00:07:52.480 --> 00:07:53.800
or fire burning fields—

00:07:55.199 --> 00:07:56.680
will be reduced to nothing.

00:08:01.959 --> 00:08:02.959
You brought me

00:08:02.959 --> 00:08:04.639
a brat meant to target me,

00:08:06.040 --> 00:08:07.839
and expect me to keep her?

00:08:09.399 --> 00:08:10.480
You're asking for death.

00:08:14.199 --> 00:08:15.000
Ah!

00:08:24.959 --> 00:08:25.879
Child, run!

00:08:26.279 --> 00:08:27.279
Run!

00:08:27.439 --> 00:08:28.600
Run, child!

00:08:29.120 --> 00:08:29.800
Don't look back!

00:08:29.920 --> 00:08:30.720
Kill her!

00:08:31.439 --> 00:08:31.839
Run!

00:08:31.959 --> 00:08:33.799
So this is the secret Xiao Duo hid.

00:08:34.799 --> 00:08:35.399
Her power

00:08:35.399 --> 00:08:37.000
can even nullify Shen Jingshi's power.

00:08:39.440 --> 00:08:41.000
I always said you were a monster.

00:08:41.159 --> 00:08:42.360
Had your parents send you away.

00:08:42.799 --> 00:08:43.600
Go on, leave.

00:08:44.120 --> 00:08:45.120
We can't handle you.

00:09:10.399 --> 00:09:11.200
Okay.

00:09:12.279 --> 00:09:13.080
I won't cry.

00:09:14.519 --> 00:09:15.759
Xiao Duo, you can't leave now.

00:09:20.399 --> 00:09:21.200
Come on, Xiao Duo.

00:09:21.799 --> 00:09:23.200
I'll take you to eat something tasty.

00:09:25.200 --> 00:09:25.840
Let's go.

00:09:36.039 --> 00:09:36.600
Xiao Duo

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:37.480
Go inside first, okay?

00:09:38.000 --> 00:09:39.200
Go lie down and rest a bit.

00:09:39.480 --> 00:09:40.759
I'll come find you soon.